		<img class="pic lazyload" data-src="/system/articles/articleshows/25426/indexMediumPc2/25426.jpg?1460542897" alt="咖啡、巧克力、红酒和奶酪，减肥的时候也别戒掉它们">
		
		<p class="category">
			<img src="/system/categories/iconwhites/19/medium/19.png?1411569539" alt="时尚">
			<span>时尚</span>
		</p>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-bd">
		<h1 class="smart-dotdotdot">咖啡、巧克力、红酒和奶酪，减肥的时候也别戒掉它们</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-ft  clearfix">
		<span class="smart-date" data-originDate="2016-04-14 07:01:50 +0800"></span>
		<div class="ribbon">
				<span class="iconfont icon-message">5</span>
